He's a two-year-old thoroughbred,
won four in a row.

156
00:15:32,311 --> 00:15:35,542
You know I race quarter horses.
I got no interest in thoroughbreds.

157
00:15:35,615 --> 00:15:39,847
He's a stakes winner, just voted
the best two-year-old in Canada.

158
00:15:39,919 --> 00:15:41,250
