as a three-year-old.

163
00:15:51,230 --> 00:15:52,720
That's crazy.

164
00:15:52,798 --> 00:15:55,995
<i>But the kicker is he's eligible to run</i>
<i>the Juvenile Breeders' Cup.</i>

165
00:15:56,068 --> 00:15:59,504
