191
00:18:02,161 --> 00:18:04,186
-Come on, buddy.
-Come here, boy.

192
00:18:15,608 --> 00:18:17,337
Sure got a mind of his own.

193
00:18:23,149 --> 00:18:24,673
You seen him on the track yet?

194
00:18:25,351 --> 00:18:28,218
-I don't think it's worth it, Mark.
<i>-Well, you made the trip.</i>

195
00:18:28,287 --> 00:18:30,915
Yeah, but I just...
I don't think he's what you're after.

196
00:18:32,391 --> 00:18:34,222
He walks funny, for one.

197
