205
00:19:34,019 --> 00:19:36,613
Forget about breeding. This one's a runner.

206
00:19:37,957 --> 00:19:39,754
You sure he's sound?

207
00:19:39,825 --> 00:19:42,020
<i>There's not a pimple on him, Mark.</i>

208
00:19:43,429 --> 00:19:44,896
You want this horse.

209
00:19:48,834 --> 00:19:51,564
All right, sit tight. I'm on my way to Doc's.

210
00:19:52,905 --> 00:19:55,237
<i>Come on, we always talked about</i>
<i>owning a thoroughbred together.</i>

211
00:19:55,307 --> 00:19:57,969
Breeders' Cup is in California in 10 days.

212
00:19:58,410 --> 00:20:00,275
If we wanna do this, we gotta get moving.

213
00:20:00,346 --> 00:20:02,678
Four hundred seems like a lot of money.

214
00:20:02,748 --> 00:20:05,376
Hell, if he just runs second,
we got our money back.

215
00:20:05,451 --> 00:20:07,749
And if he don't run second,

216
00:20:07,820 --> 00:20:10,584
we bought ourselves a very expensive pony.

217
00:20:11,957 --> 00:20:15,484
You know I don't like taking leaps like this,
sight unseen.

218
00:20:15,561 --> 00:20:17,392
He's already won $300,000.

219
00:20:18,063 --> 00:20:19,121
