220
00:20:20,533 --> 00:20:23,161
I'll tell you what then. I'll buy him.

221
00:20:24,703 --> 00:20:28,366
I'll buy him myself.
You like what you see, I'll cut you in.

222
00:20:32,878 --> 00:20:35,711
Shit. I'm in.

223
00:20:53,866 --> 00:20:55,891
